{\listtext	\'95	}6 pounds {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/potato/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 \ul \ulc2 Idaho potatoes}}, peeled and quartered\
{\listtext	\'95	}Salt\
